																		Press Your Space-Face Close To Mine, Love
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6479803); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6479803&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610226982" alt="HarryBlank" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6479803)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6479803); return false;" >HarryBlank</a></span> <span class="odate time_1601324534 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">28 Sep 2020 20:22</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4784073">
									

<p>I did tell you we were going to the sun.</p>
<p>All the credit in the world to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-reach" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1779895); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1779895&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601330219" alt="Dr Reach" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1779895)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-reach" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1779895); return false;">Dr Reach</a></span> for 179 and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3187823); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3187823&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601330219" alt="CadaverCommander" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3187823)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3187823); return false;">CadaverCommander</a></span> for 1233!</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;I&nbsp;love&nbsp;these&nbsp;characters&nbsp;so&nbsp;damn&nbsp;much</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;I&nbsp;hope&nbsp;you&nbsp;love&nbsp;them&nbsp;too,&nbsp;to&nbsp;an&nbsp;uncomfortable&nbsp;degree</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>So, uh, nobody's put these two together before? <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Except in that one April Fools' Day joke.</span></p>
<p>Sauelsuesor is the best thing in Series I. Have I read the entire Series? No. Do I have to? No. Honestly, I think I knew her article was the best part of the Series the moment I read it. What could be better? That's right, nothing. She's perfect, and Dr. Reach hit it <em>wayyyy</em> out of the park.</p>
<p>Moon Champion might just be the best thing in Series II. CadaverCommander <em>also</em> hit it out of the park. I'll get to have more fun with him (Moon Champion, not CadaverCommander) when he's on Earth, and he can do more than float around and talk funny, but hopefully this little teaser has left you completely unable to picture how our storyline's going to move forward.</p>
<p>It'll be more fun for me if it comes as a surprise to you.</p>
<p>Sauelsuesor's full name comes from <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/forum/t-1048694/scp-2115#post-2159263">this</a> probably non-canonical but great post by Dr. Reach, and the information about her weighing rather a lot comes from <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/forum/t-13259911/scp-179-weighs-over-ten-quadrillion-kilograms">this</a> post by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ruengies-elaj" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6193532); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6193532&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601330219" alt="Ruengies_Elaj" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6193532)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ruengies-elaj" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6193532); return false;">Ruengies_Elaj</a></span>.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>Special thanks to TEAM RR BEST TEAM: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/karakatt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5950867); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5950867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601330219" alt="KaraKatt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5950867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/karakatt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5950867); return false;">KaraKatt</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009022); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3009022&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601330219" alt="not_a_seagull" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3009022)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009022); return false;">not_a_seagull</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-pighead" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3242824); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3242824&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601330219" alt="The Pighead" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3242824)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-pighead" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3242824); return false;">The Pighead</a></span>, and of course to Constant Reader <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4558017); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4558017&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601330219" alt="Grigori Karpin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4558017)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4558017); return false;">Grigori Karpin</a></span>.</p>
<p>Oh, and that not-particularly-complicated sun logo is just yours truly dicking around with our existing imagery.</p>

